| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1151 — Mass File Rename (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ac1ea8b9-88ec-56d0-a7e4-f46d3dd105d1"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
